• You have a playful curiosity about the world. You enjoy thinking in nonlinear, outside-the-box ways and often have a mischievous sense of fun. 

• You may use wit, jokes and playful banter to connect with others, lift their spirits or put them at ease. Bringing levity and laughter to situations is natural for you. 

• You tend to not take yourself too seriously. You appreciate the lighter side of life and embracing the moment with a sense of joy and fun. 

• You may be skilled at divergent thinking, ad-libbing, improvising and creating in spontaneous ways. Rules and procedures don't bog you down.

• You get energized from imaginative, unstructured activities and conversations. Routine and mundane tasks can drain you.

